Wii Video Mode Changer
================================

[ENGLISH]

- How to use Wii VMC:

Just drag the "main.dol" file onto the Wii VMC exectuable and use one of the
different patchers availables.

If you don't know which patcher to use, use the "Smart patcher".


[SPANISH]

- Como usar Wii VMC:

Simplemente arrastra el fichero "main.dol" al ejecutable del Wii VMC y usa
uno de los diferentes parcheadores disponibles.

Si no sabes que parcheador usar, utiliza el "Smart patcher" (parcheador inteligente).

